import { CampaingSummaryModel } from '../../../../models/campaing-summary'
import { FunilContainer, TitleLine, TimeLine, TextLine, TimeLineDot, Dots, Dot, Line, TitleStep, LineContainer, TextStep, InfoNumber, InfoText } from './styles'

interface Props {
    campaingSummary: CampaingSummaryModel
    color: string
  }
  
  const FunilLine = ({ campaingSummary, color }: Props) => {
    return (
      <FunilContainer>
        <TitleLine style={{color: color}}>
          <TitleStep>Noticias</TitleStep>
          <TitleStep>Compra</TitleStep>
          <TitleStep>Checkout</TitleStep>
          <TitleStep>Pagos</TitleStep>
        </TitleLine>

        <TimeLine>
          <Dots>
            <TimeLineDot>
              <Dot style={{background: color}}></Dot>
            </TimeLineDot>
            
            <TimeLineDot>
              <Dot style={{background: color}}></Dot>
            </TimeLineDot>

            <TimeLineDot>
              <Dot style={{background: color}}></Dot>
            </TimeLineDot>

            <TimeLineDot>
              <Dot style={{background: color}}></Dot>
            </TimeLineDot>
          </Dots>
          
          <LineContainer>
            <Line style={{borderColor: color}}></Line>
          </LineContainer>
        </TimeLine>

        <TextLine>
          <TextStep style={{color: color}}>
            <InfoNumber>{campaingSummary.totalClicks}</InfoNumber>
            <InfoText>Pessoas</InfoText>
          </TextStep>

          <TextStep style={{color: color}}>
            {campaingSummary.totalProductPage}
            <InfoText>Pessoas</InfoText>
            {JSON.stringify(campaingSummary.totalProductPage/campaingSummary.totalClicks*100).substring(0,4)}%
          </TextStep>

          <TextStep style={{color: color}}>
            {campaingSummary.totalCheckoutPage}
            <InfoText>Pessoas</InfoText>
            {campaingSummary.totalProductPage? JSON.stringify(campaingSummary.totalCheckoutPage/campaingSummary.totalProductPage*100).substring(0,4): 0}%
          </TextStep>

          <TextStep style={{color: '#ec8f4d'}}>
            {campaingSummary.totalPaidClicks}
            <InfoText>Pessoas</InfoText>
            {campaingSummary.totalCheckoutPage? JSON.stringify(campaingSummary.totalPaidClicks/campaingSummary.totalCheckoutPage*100).substring(0,4) : 0}%
          </TextStep>
        </TextLine>
      </FunilContainer>
    )
  }
  
  export default FunilLine
